         function InsertNewsletter() {            
             var email = "";
             var name = "";
             var surname = "";
             var title = "";
             var result = true;
             var count = 0;
             var msg="";
             var re = /^(([^<>()[\]\\.,;:\s@\"]+(\.[^<>()[\]\\.,;:\s@\"]+)*)|(\".+\"))@((\[[0-9]{1,3}\.[0-9]{1,3}\.[0-9]{1,3}\.[0-9]{1,3}\])|(([a-zA-Z\-0-9]+\.)+[a-zA-Z]{2,}))$/;
             if (document.getElementById("TextBox_Newsletter_Email")) {
                 document.getElementById('TextBox_Newsletter_Email').style.border = '1px solid #afafaf';
                 if (re.test(document.getElementById("TextBox_Newsletter_Email").value) == false) {
                     document.getElementById('TextBox_Newsletter_Email').style.border = '1px solid red';
                     msg = "Wrong format!";
                     result = false;
                 }
                 if (document.getElementById("TextBox_Newsletter_Email").value == "") {
                     document.getElementById('TextBox_Newsletter_Email').style.border = '1px solid red';
                     msg = "Insert e-mail!"
                     result = false;
                 }
                 if (result == false) {
                     count = count + 1;
                 }
             }
             if (document.getElementById("TextBox_Newsletter_Name")) {
                 document.getElementById('TextBox_Newsletter_Name').style.border = '1px solid #afafaf';
                 if (document.getElementById("TextBox_Newsletter_Name").value == "") {
                     document.getElementById('TextBox_Newsletter_Name').style.border = '1px solid red';
                     msg = "Insert name!"
                     result = false;
                     count = count + 1;
                 }
             }
             if (document.getElementById("TextBox_Newsletter_Surname")) {
                 document.getElementById('TextBox_Newsletter_Surname').style.border = '1px solid #afafaf';
                 if (document.getElementById("TextBox_Newsletter_Surname").value == "") {
                     document.getElementById('TextBox_Newsletter_Surname').style.border = '1px solid red';
                     msg = "Insert surname!"
                     result = false;
                     count = count + 1;
                 }
             }            
             if (result) {
                 email = document.getElementById("TextBox_Newsletter_Email").value;
                 name = document.getElementById("TextBox_Newsletter_Name").value;
                 surname = document.getElementById("TextBox_Newsletter_Surname").value;
                 title = document.getElementById("Select_Newsletter_Treatment").value;                
                 $.get("/handlers/InsertSubscriptionNewsletter.ashx?ts=" + new Date().getTime() + "&name=" + name + "&surname=" + surname + "&email=" + email + "&title=" + title, { idioma: 'ferienwohnung' }, function (data) {
                     if (data == "1") {
                         alert("Suscription succesfull!");
                     }
                     else {
                         alert("An error has occurred while processing your request!");
                     }
                 });
                 
             }
             else {
                 if (count < 2) {
                     alert(msg);
                 }
                 else {
                     alert("Insert values!");
                 }
             }
         }

           <script type="text/javascript">
            $(document).ready(function () {
         SetUpArrivalDeparturePickers('#startdate', '#enddate', '/img/calendar.png', '', "Von:", "Bis:");
         $('#startdate').focus(function () {
             $('#startdate').datepicker('show');
         });
         $('#enddate').focus(function () {
             $('#enddate').datepicker('show');
         });
     });
     initAutoComplete();    
     function GoHomeQuickSearch(argLang)
     {        
         if ($("[id$=TextBox_Link_Destino]").val() == "") {            
             redirectListingBtn(argLang,'/ferienwohnung/alle-reiseziele');
         }
         else {           
             redirectListingBtn(argLang);
         }
     }   
     function getDaysOfStay() {
         if (('') == "") {
             return 1;
         }
         else {
             return ('');
         }
     }
     function initAutoComplete() {
         var destino_id;
         var destino_nombre;
         var destino_tipo;
         var destino_link;
         var destino_checkin;
         var destino_checkout;
         $('#quick_search1_TextBox_Destination').autocomplete({
             source: function (request, response) {
                 $.ajax({
                     url: "/handlers/autocomplete.ashx?idioma=ferienwohnung",
                         dataType: "json",
                         data: {
                             name_startsWith: request.term
                         },
                         success: function (data) {
                             response($.map(data, function (item) {
                                 return {
                                     label: item.Destino_nombre,
                                     value: item.Destino_nombre,
                                     value2: item.Destino_id,
                                     value3: item.Destino_tipo,
                                     value4: item.Destino_link
                                 }
                             }));
                         }
                     });
                 },
             minLength: 1,
             autoFocus: true,
             select: function (event, ui) {
                 destino_nombre = ui.item.label;
                 destino_id = ui.item.value2;
                 destino_tipo = ui.item.value3;
                 destino_link = ui.item.value4;
             },
             open: function () {
                 destino_nombre = null;
                 destino_id = null;
                 destino_tipo = null;
                 destino_link = null;
                 $(this).removeClass("ui-corner-all").addClass("ui-corner-top");
             },
             close: function () {
                 $(this).removeClass("ui-corner-top").addClass("ui-corner-all");
                 if (destino_nombre != null) {
                     document.getElementById('quick_search1_TextBox_Destination').value = $.trim(destino_nombre);
                         document.getElementById('quick_search1_TextBox_Link_Destino').value = destino_link;
 
                     }
                     else {
                         document.getElementById('quick_search1_TextBox_Destination').value = "";
                         document.getElementById('quick_search1_TextBox_Link_Destino').value = "";
                     }
                 }
         });
             document.getElementById('quick_search1_TextBox_Destination').placeholder = "Ihr Reiseziel";
     }
     $('#quick_search1_TextBox_Destination').click(function () {
         $('#quick_search1_TextBox_Destination').autocomplete("search", "top4areas");
         this.setSelectionRange(0, this.value.length)
     });
 
     $("#Link_ClearDates").click(function (ev) {
         ev.preventDefault();
     });
